  "None suggested yet": "Ninguna sugerencia aún",
  "After the AI responds, a separate quiet API call generates the tracker JSON independently. Expect ~250–300s total per message (narrative + wait + tracker).": "Después de la respuesta, una llamada silenciosa genera el JSON. ~250–300s/mensaje.",
  "✓ Single API call — typically ~100–120s total": "✓ Una llamada API — ~100–120s",
  "✓ No profile switching — eliminates message deletion risk": "✓ Sin cambio de perfil — sin riesgo de borrado",
  "✓ AI has full narrative context for accurate tracking": "✓ La IA tiene contexto narrativo completo",
  "✓ 2–3× faster than Separate mode in practice": "✓ 2–3× más rápido que Separado",
  "✗ Uses tokens from the main response budget (~1,700 tokens for tracker)": "✗ Usa tokens del presupuesto principal (~1.700)",
  "✗ May slightly reduce narrative length on token-limited models": "✗ Puede reducir ligeramente la narrativa",
