  "✓ Dedicated token budget for tracker output": "✓ Presupuesto dedicado para el rastreador",
  "✓ Can use a different connection profile/preset": "✓ Puede usar otro perfil/preset",
  "✗ Two API calls per message — 2–3× slower than Together mode": "✗ Dos llamadas API — 2–3× más lento",
  "✗ ~12s dead time between calls (chat save + preset switching)": "✗ ~12s de espera entre llamadas",
  "✗ Tracker prompt is ~10K+ tokens at 8 context msgs — reduce to 3–4 for speed": "✗ Prompt ~10K+ con 8 msgs — reduzca a 3–4",
  "✗ Profile switching can cause message deletion (race condition with other extensions)": "✗ El cambio de perfil puede causar borrado",
  "✗ Embeds previous snapshot into narrative call (~1.9K tokens) unless Embed snapshots = 0": "✗ Incluye snapshot anterior (~1.9K) salvo 0",
  "How many recent messages to include when generating tracker updates.": "Cuántos mensajes recientes incluir al actualizar.",
  "Separate mode only — Together mode uses ST's full context automatically.": "Solo modo Separado — Junto usa el contexto de ST.",
  "Fastest. Good for simple 1-on-1 scenes (~5K token prompt)": "Más rápido. Para escenas 1 a 1 (~5K)",
  "Balanced. Recommended for most scenes (~8–12K tokens)": "Equilibrado. Para la mayoría (~8–12K)",
  "Better continuity for complex multi-character scenes (~12–20K tokens)": "Mejor continuidad para escenas complejas (~12–20K)",
  "Maximum context but significantly slower and more expensive": "Máximo contexto pero mucho más lento y costoso",
  "This is the biggest factor in Separate mode speed. At 8 msgs your tracker prompt is ~10K tokens — doubling roughly doubles generation time. Lower values (3–4) can cut tracker time by 40–60%.": "Mayor factor de velocidad. Con 8 msgs ~10K — duplicar duplica el tiempo. 3–4 reduce 40–60%.",
  "Separate mode only.": "Solo modo Separado.",
  "How many times to retry if the tracker API call returns invalid JSON.": "Reintentos si el API devuelve JSON inválido.",
  "Built-in preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Optimized for structured JSON output on GLM-5.": "Preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Para JSON en GLM-5.",
  "Embed recent scene snapshots into the narrative conversation context so the AI can reference tracker state while writing. Only applies in Separate mode. The tracker's own API call always receives the previous snapshot regardless of this setting.": "Incrusta snapshots en el contexto narrativo. Solo Separado. El rastreador siempre recibe el anterior.",
  "Each embedded snapshot adds ~1.9K tokens to your narrative prompt. Set to 0 to eliminate this overhead — the tracker API call still receives previous state independently. Set to 1 for narrative continuity (AI remembers scene details). Values above 1 are rarely beneficial.": "Cada snapshot +~1.9K. 0 para eliminar. 1 para continuidad. Más de 1 rara vez útil.",
  "Injected as invisible context — AI treats it as authoritative background info. Best for continuity without polluting the conversation.": "Inyectado como contexto invisible — tratado como info autorizada.",
  "Appears as if the user said it — some models respond more attentively.": "Aparece como dicho por el usuario — algunos modelos responden mejor.",
